      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，提交评价给5分，前面两个给4分。另外检查一下section的标题，\"Go to product\"可能不够准确，应该是\"Go to product\"还是\"Browse product\"？",
      "elements_involved": [
